# Budget Intelligent

Budget Intelligent is a financial management web application that helps users track their income and expenses, analyze their spending habits, and optimize their budget.

The project provides a clear and structured view of personal finances through a simple and intuitive interface with analytical tools.

---

## Features

- User authentication (login / registration)
- Income and expense management
- Transaction categorization
- Financial dashboard with statistics
- Monthly budget tracking
- Spending habit analysis
- Budget limit alerts (if applicable)
- Data export (optional depending on version)

---

## Technologies Used

- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: PHP
- Database: MySQL
- Tools: Git, GitHub

